uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.editors.mail

Class AbstractVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.AbstractContexed
      • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.editors.mail.AbstractVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Contexed, Visitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActionMessageVisitor, ContentMessageVisitor, DeDupVisitor, IsMessageVisitor, MimeStreamDataVisitor, PrefixVisitor

    public class AbstractVisitor
extends AbstractContexed
implements Visitor
    Implementation of the Visitor interface with default implementations of methods to make it easier to produce classes that implement the interface correctly. Essentially each method does nothing and all recursion is enabled
